April 20, 1949.

Miscellaneous Order.

No. 506. United States ex rel. Johnson v. Watkins, District Director of Immigration and Naturalization.

Certiorari, 336 U. S. 924, to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit. Shaughnessy, Acting District Director of Immigration and Naturalization, substituted as party respondent, per stipulation of counsel, on motion of Gunther Jacobson for the petitioner.
